a_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The parties agree to the provisions specified in this Agreement and, as applicable,  the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA), the Michigan Identity Theft Protection Act, and all other applicable public health, research, and confidentiality laws.The data elements to be provided  to  MDHHS  under this Agreement will be consistent with the required  element designated by MDHHS  and as  identified in the Michigan Administrative Code R. 325.125 et. seq .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 568, "end_char_idx": 1045, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5051a29a-5365-4b59-a65f-51c84269092c": {"__data__": {"id_": "5051a29a-5365-4b59-a65f-51c84269092c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "33e3ea15-e993-46be-afec-16f3e62b7465", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6c72473c10519fee13c5374751aeef5abea3cae6743793678a22716553ce9104", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "b2b4126b-8d29-43ff-aeeb-ff3d9eedc3cc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f60ef1ab184220250805a0db6a952c1fbc9c3ae90ef3c7a7904479faabb7d808", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "9c8bba6d-b165-42ae-b2f3-630a26f5d29d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a7d046a791a89c73ed66555a6074ad06ef9ba77550dafebd8a3bc2d8929573e0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The data provided to MDHHS  will be used  only for purposes of the Michigan Trauma Registry, consistent with Part 209 of the Public Health Code and the Michigan Administrative Code R 325.125 through 325.138.Data in the Michigan Trauma Registry will be disclosed to Regional Trauma Networks through  access to the Michigan Trauma Registry database.  Individuals granted access to the Michigan Trauma Registry database will be required to execute user agreements with MDHHS.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1049, "end_char_idx": 1521, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "9c8bba6d-b165-42ae-b2f3-630a26f5d29d": {"__data__": {"id_": "9c8bba6d-b165-42ae-b2f3-630a26f5d29d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "33e3ea15-e993-46be-afec-16f3e62b7465", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6c72473c10519fee13c5374751aeef5abea3cae6743793678a22716553ce9104", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "5051a29a-5365-4b59-a65f-51c84269092c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "60341fb17cdd27c8c798048cc33fd1d2ea42756e2917976ebf8cab46124e12a7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a2f89056-2c76-4764-95f0-c15a9278070f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7afc180b92659d72e27540ea34d341d19b2962e29d5434dcb10f423b00e2eeaf", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "With regard to the data disclosed to MDHHS under this Agreement, the MDHHS agrees to:\n\n1. Use and disclose the data only in accordance with this Agreement, or as otherwise\n\nauthorized by law; 2.\n\n Notify Reporting Entity within a reasonable time prior to disclosing data that is required by law so that Reporting Entity may have an opportunity to object to such disclosure if necessary;\n\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1523, "end_char_idx": 1913, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a2f89056-2c76-4764-95f0-c15a9278070f": {"__data__": {"id_": "a2f89056-2c76-4764-95f0-c15a9278070f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "33e3ea15-e993-46be-afec-16f3e62b7465", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6c72473c10519fee13c5374751aeef5abea3cae6743793678a22716553ce9104", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "9c8bba6d-b165-42ae-b2f3-630a26f5d29d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a7d046a791a89c73ed66555a6074ad06ef9ba77550dafebd8a3bc2d8929573e0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "e2bbd92c-62d6-45e3-b106-447b9181d615", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e5a7bda51c1a2cc2534b9dd2f123db9263f00ed9829bccb62ec3c3c70fed2543", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Limit access to these  data only to those  MDHHS  employees  whose job responsibilities\n\nrequire access to the information; 4.\n\n Use appropriate safeguards to prevent the use or disclosure of the information other than as provided by this Agreement;\n\n5.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1916, "end_char_idx": 2169, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e2bbd92c-62d6-45e3-b106-447b9181d615": {"__data__": {"id_": "e2bbd92c-62d6-45e3-b106-447b9181d615", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "33e3ea15-e993-46be-afec-16f3e62b7465", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6c72473c10519fee13c5374751aeef5abea3cae6743793678a22716553ce9104", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a2f89056-2c76-4764-95f0-c15a9278070f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7afc180b92659d72e27540ea34d341d19b2962e29d5434dcb10f423b00e2eeaf", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "156f84ee-3dfc-4915-b80b-8ed5d7a63bbb", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "2468b3541810c4f1724842b7e013c12d2ca41f211cfcea5a470fb33317dfa8e2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Report to the Reporting Entity  within  ten (10) business days of discovery any actual or suspected  inappropriate  use,  disclosure, or breach  of information from the Michigan Trauma Registry that involves data submitted under this Agreement;\n\n6.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2172, "end_char_idx": 2420, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "156f84ee-3dfc-4915-b80b-8ed5d7a63bbb": {"__data__": {"id_": "156f84ee-3dfc-4915-b80b-8ed5d7a63bbb", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "33e3ea15-e993-46be-afec-16f3e62b7465", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6c72473c10519fee13c5374751aeef5abea3cae6743793678a22716553ce9104", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "e2bbd92c-62d6-45e3-b106-447b9181d615", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e5a7bda51c1a2cc2534b9dd2f123db9263f00ed9829bccb62ec3c3c70fed2543", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "b26dba57-53c3-4631-b6ff-72099796c4f0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "87476a75d3375064f33b0a0adb824214646383c441929cff511943d849812611", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Make no attempt to identify or contact the individuals or entities within the data provided unless  permitted in Part 209 of the Public Health Code  or the Michigan Administrative Code R 325.125 through 325.138;\n7-9-2015 Final Page 1 of 2\n\n7. Destroy all originals and copies of potentially identifiable information, in any format,\n\n in accordance with industry standards when no longer needed.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2423, "end_char_idx": 2817, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, 